## Summary Rules

- `overview`: 2-3 sentences describing what the video is about.
- `key_topics`: 3-8 core topics discussed.
- `speakers`: map speaker IDs to roles (e.g. "host", "guest", or names if inferable).
- `title`: short descriptive title if inferable, else empty string.
- `domain`: content domain (e.g. "AI research podcast").

## Glossary Rules

- Include ONLY domain-specific, high-impact terms (technical jargon, proper nouns, abbreviations).
- Skip common words a general audience already knows (bug, API, GPU, model, data).
- Values must be suggested {{ target_lang }} translations.
- Keep proper nouns in original spelling when they should not be translated (e.g. whisper.cpp).
- 5-30 entries typical; quality over quantity.

